{"tid":369494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[神棍塔羅]隨心占一占 (2)","createTime":"2017-08-22T11:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T05:34:55.000Z","uid":70910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46e0cb87b8cbb6409415b9af0695aa53ab57ae46","tid":369494,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"有問題想問的話，請跟格式留言<br />\n知道結果後俾feedback<br />\n<br />\n占前必看<br />\n1.時間性問題唔占(e.g. 幾時有男朋友，幾時遇到真愛)<br />\n2.生死 健康不占<br />\n3.太長遠不占，最好一年內<br />\n4.問題之外，可以講低一啲你認為有助占卜既背景資料<br />\n<br />\n格式<br />\n你的名字: <br />\n問題:<br />\n<br />\n每日都會占5個或以上，如果留言4日都未見有回覆，可輕輕一推"},{"pid":"79f4f45a44e705ecbbea6294a257822112ae61a6","tid":369494,"uid":81262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"名：k <br />\n返工果到有冇女仔對我有好感？ 謝謝"},{"pid":"66fa3bcb4a82969f937989c318403803378fc7a6","tid":369494,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc645904d7a34e064274004b7e8ffe4357a584c9","tid":369494,"uid":91105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"名：瑩 女<br />\n問題： 想問下我今個月有冇機會拍拖"},{"pid":"e16fb02ea508e44ae2af98fe59ce07fbce03c339","tid":369494,"uid":27843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a761fbe3e54f59fb648f583a9c8e89f26d958aa2","tid":369494,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係呢到截一截先<br />\n各位新問卜者唔好留住<br />\n我地清晒舊數先會再占<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"364ad68f212dc44e648bf1c81547f73a44f74aa4","tid":369494,"uid":46404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=