blockquote>名字：德<br />\n問題： 鍾意一個同事年幾,但關係成日好似過山車咁,一時超熱一時超冷,永遠唔明佢諗咩,雖然一直堅持住,但已經開始覺得累,好想放低,只係驚會唔會其實只差少少就得<br />\n<br />\n所以想知如果繼續堅持會點,放棄既話未來又會唔會遇到好對象<br />\n利申A0</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就咁睇<br />\n堅持真係有成功既一刻<br />\n不過中間要經歷多次低谷 <br />\n暫時咁睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">放棄<br />\n應該都唔會遇到心儀既人嫁喇<br />\n埋頭苦幹咁做野 扮唔記得人</span></blockquote><br />\n係咪2段野黎<br />\n即係如果唔驚無限心碎既話,捱得過就仲有希望?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你問兩個選擇既未來麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以咁講 希望在明天麻</blockquote><br />\n問題係而家個低谷位都唔係好知點解決<br />\n其實佢點睇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a22c08b7593a781ce89d47dd901769cf6260a1e","tid":369494,"uid":135196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"大師，想問多兩個問題<br />\n1）我黎緊讀書會如何？（會唔會讀得成？成績好唔好咁）<br />\n2）將來工作發展會係咩行業（十五十六未揀到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"3907ea7ea28f356fc695fb758ed794388d86e4ae","tid":369494,"uid":10515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"名：嵐<br />\n問題:同佢有冇機會好返，定佢已經唔想再理"},{"pid":"8ab17d5efba767f03200b33f414642d36e37fe4b","tid":369494,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係呢到截一截先<br />\n各位新問卜者唔好留住<br />\n我地清晒舊數先會再占<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n很重要</blockquote><br />\n所以講三次</blockquote><br />\n第四次"},{"pid":"fa5a5c71e655a198b7e33cf9f7c5358fd0ccf551","tid":369494,"uid":68298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"592等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326cc50f9c6ea70